Edition:
Quote:  Hauhauism was the result of several different features, which became welded in 1863 in the form of a fanatical religion. ... The progess of Hauhauism corresponded largely with the progess of the Maori King Movement; and with the defeat of the Kingite tribes the religion became a ... negligible force.
